    "Driver not detected" : { "localizations" : { "es" : { "stringUnit" : { "state" : "translated", "value" : "Driver no detectado" } } } },
    "macOS does not expose SMART data for many USB/SAT enclosures by default. CheckMyDisk will read any external drive that smartctl can see, and can use pass-through modes such as sat, sat12, sat16, jmicron, or auto when the driver/enclosure supports them." : { "localizations" : { "es" : { "stringUnit" : { "state" : "translated", "value" : "macOS no expone datos SMART de muchas cajas USB/SAT por defecto. CheckMyDisk leerá cualquier disco externo que smartctl pueda ver, y puede usar modos pass-through como sat, sat12, sat16, jmicron o auto cuando el driver o la caja lo permitan." } } } },
    "SAT SMART Driver project" : { "localizations" : { "es" : { "stringUnit" : { "state" : "translated", "value" : "Proyecto SAT SMART Driver" } } } },
    "smartctl Backend" : { "localizations" : { "es" : { "stringUnit" : { "state" : "translated", "value" : "Backend de smartctl" } } } },
